5. Delete all records from STUDENT table.


mysql> select* from students;
+---------+------+-----+---------+--------+
| roll_no | name | age | address | gender |
+---------+------+-----+---------+--------+
|       1 | sam  |  21 | ssa     | f      |
|       2 | tom  |  25 | www     | f      |
|       3 | qam  |  21 | ssa     | m      |
|       4 | ram  |  20 | qwa     | m      |
|       5 | yam  |  23 | ped     | m      |
+---------+------+-----+---------+--------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> delete from students;
Query OK, 5 rows affected (0.04 sec)

mysql> select* from students;
Empty set (0.00 sec)






